1308
01:48:22,860 --> 01:48:26,420
 a normalno cija je javljala podatke,

1309
01:48:26,420 --> 01:48:28,200
 slušajte, tam neki Mateji

1310
01:48:28,200 --> 01:48:30,860
 se nama suprostavlja,

1311
01:48:30,860 --> 01:48:32,940
 upada nam u igru i tako dalje.

1312
01:48:32,940 --> 01:48:34,480
 On je otišao u Rusiju,

1313
01:48:34,480 --> 01:48:35,560
