1317
01:48:40,360 --> 01:48:41,400
 američka je bila negdje

1318
01:48:41,400 --> 01:48:44,080
 2,75, 3 dolara je bila po barelu,

1319
01:48:44,080 --> 01:48:45,680
 koliko on jeftinije,

1320
01:48:45,680 --> 01:48:47,140
 ali je radio bartere,

1321
01:48:47,140 --> 01:48:49,020
 Rusijima je isporučivao cijevi

1322
01:48:49,020 --> 01:48:50,000
 i sve naftovode,

1323
01:48:50,000 --> 01:48:51,480
 plinovele koje su rađeni,

1324
01:48:51,480 --> 01:48:53,240
