1335
01:49:15,160 --> 01:49:16,420
 da treba otići u Ameriku

1336
01:49:16,420 --> 01:49:17,100
 na sastanak

1337
01:49:17,100 --> 01:49:18,640
 i njegov avion

1338
01:49:18,640 --> 01:49:20,640
 se zbog sabotaže

1339
01:49:20,640 --> 01:49:21,900
 se srušio kod Milana

1340
01:49:21,900 --> 01:49:22,900
 i čovjek je ubijen.

1341
01:49:23,600 --> 01:49:25,140
 A posle toga su ubili

1342
01:49:25,140 --> 01:49:27,420
 Kennedy-a,

1343
01:49:27,420 --> 01:49:29,500
 pa su ubili Alda Mora,

1344
01:49:29,500 --> 01:49:30,220
 ako se sjeće.

1345
01:49:30,220 --> 01:49:31,400
 U Italiji, tako je, da.

1346
01:49:31,400 --> 01:49:32,500
 Neću širiti priče,

1347
01:49:32,500 --> 01:49:33,960
 tu su Brigate Rose

1348
01:49:33,960 --> 01:49:35,600
 i Badermain,

1349
01:49:35,600 --> 01:49:38,360
 hof i sve te tajne organizacije

1350
01:49:38,360 --> 01:49:39,520
 koje su terorističke,

1351
01:49:39,520 --> 01:49:41,880
 koje su operirale.

1352
01:49:41,880 --> 01:49:45,520
 A koje su ove tajne organizacije

1353
01:49:45,520 --> 01:49:46,780
 i obaveštajne službe

1354
01:49:46,780 --> 01:49:48,360
 financirale

1355
01:49:48,360 --> 01:49:50,220
 i s njima u stvari dirigirale,

1356
01:49:50,220 --> 01:49:51,680
 a da one to nisu ni znale

1357
01:49:51,680 --> 01:49:53,000
 i one su ih koristili

1358
01:49:53,000 --> 01:49:53,960
 za sve te posle

1359
01:49:53,960 --> 01:49:54,860
 i tako dalje.

1360
01:49:54,860 --> 01:49:56,000
 Vidite koliko je taj,

1361
01:49:56,000 --> 01:49:56,960
 a to sve,

1362
01:49:56,960 --> 01:49:58,160
 ovo što pričamo,

1363
01:49:58,160 --> 01:49:59,860
 su te sve te sorele.

1364
01:49:59,860 --> 01:50:01,600
 Znate što,

1365
01:50:01,600 --> 01:50:03,120
 ostali ste mi dužni Davos,

1366
01:50:03,120 --> 01:50:04,320
 odnosno ostali smo dužni

1367
01:50:04,320 --> 01:50:05,220
 nas dvoje Davos

1368
01:50:05,220 --> 01:50:06,180
 s kojim smo krenuli.

1369
01:50:06,180 --> 01:50:08,120
 Što je ove godine zapravo

1370
01:50:08,120 --> 01:50:10,120
 tamo rečeno?

1371
01:50:10,120 --> 01:50:12,480
 Što je glavna poruka?

1372
01:50:12,480 --> 01:50:13,540
 To bih voljela da,

1373
01:50:13,540 --> 01:50:15,040
 evo, pred kraj ovog

1374
01:50:15,040 --> 01:50:16,420
 prilično dugog podcasta,

1375
01:50:16,420 --> 01:50:18,760
 da malo ljudima objasnimo

1376
01:50:18,760 --> 01:50:20,600
