01:50:27,880 --> 01:50:29,300
 koji je radio sve

1385
01:50:29,300 --> 01:50:30,900
 po naputku

1386
01:50:30,900 --> 01:50:32,660
 međunarodne finanske oligarhije.

1387
01:50:32,660 --> 01:50:34,780
 I to su

1388
01:50:34,780 --> 01:50:36,220
 vrlo važne stvari

1389
01:50:36,220 --> 01:50:37,600
 koje se odvijaju danas,

1390
01:50:37,600 --> 01:50:38,860
 jer on je napisao

1391
01:50:38,860 --> 01:50:39,520
 i tri knjige,

1392
01:50:39,520 --> 01:50:40,460
 a to je jedna knjiga

1393
01:50:40,460 --> 01:50:41,140
 je bilo, znači,

1394
01:50:41,140 --> 01:50:43,280
 četvrta industrijska revolucija,

1395
01:50:43,280 --> 01:50:45,240
 druga knjiga je bila

1396
01:50:45,240 --> 01:50:47,320
 strateški partneri,

1397
01:50:47,900 --> 01:50:49,800
 i treća knjiga je bilo

1398
01:50:49,800 --> 01:50:50,780
 COVID-19

1399
01:50:50,780 --> 01:50:51,320
 i

1400
01:50:51,320 --> 01:50:55,700
 Big Reset.

1401
01:50:55,700 --> 01:50:57,340
 Što je

1402
01:50:57,340 --> 01:50:59,580
 četvrta industrijska revolucija,

1403
01:50:59,580 --> 01:51:00,720
 to nam je svima poznato.

1404
01:51:00,720 --> 01:51:01,020
 Znači,

1405
01:51:01,020 --> 01:51:02,520
 automatizacija, robotizacija,

1406
01:51:02,520 --> 01:51:02,960
 ovo sve,

1407
01:51:02,960 --> 01:51:04,500
 nova tehnologija koja ide,

1408
01:51:04,500 --> 01:51:06,200
 tvornice danas rade,

1409
01:51:06,200 --> 01:51:07,880
 svi je automatizirani

1410
01:51:07,880 --> 01:51:09,440
 i to je okej.

1411
01:51:09,440 --> 01:51:11,520
 Ajde, svima nam je to jasno.

1412
01:51:13,100 --> 01:51:15,300
 To oni govore,

1413
01:51:15,300 --> 01:51:19,100
 da čovjek se mora prilagoditi

1414
01:51:19,100 --> 01:51:20,820
 tim tehnološkim uvjetima

1415
01:51:20,820 --> 01:51:23,860
 i da se to treba izmijeniti čovjek.

1416
01:51:23,860 --> 01:51:27,840
 Znači, oni stavljaju akcent na čovjeka.

1417
01:51:27,840 --> 01:51:30,380
 Druga stvar je ova druga knjiga

1418
01:51:30,380 --> 01:51:31,660
 u kojoj on govori,

1419
01:51:31,660 --> 01:51:33,080
 a to je strateški partner.

1420
01:51:33,080 --> 01:51:35,480
 Ja kad sam pisao ovu političku bibliju,

1421
01:51:35,480 --> 01:51:37,840
 onda ja sam našao podatak

1422
01:51:37,840 --> 01:51:39,040
 u Britanskoj arhivi

1423
01:51:39,040 --> 01:51:40,760
