1424
01:51:40,760 --> 01:51:42,980
 gdje Britanci navode

1425
01:51:42,980 --> 01:51:45,860
 taj termin strateški partner.

1426
01:51:45,860 --> 01:51:47,980
 A on je lukavo uzeo to sebi

1427
01:51:47,980 --> 01:51:49,640
 za naslov svoje knjige.

1428
01:51:49,640 --> 01:51:51,520
 I tu je spomenuo ovih,

1429
01:51:51,520 --> 01:51:54,500
 navodi tih sto korporacija

1430
01:51:54,500 --> 01:51:57,720
 i sto najvećih banaka.

1431
01:51:57,720 --> 01:51:58,640
 Jer naravno,

1432
01:51:58,640 --> 01:52:00,780
 sav biznis prate financije,

1433
01:52:00,780 --> 01:52:03,920
 a banke su financijski prateoci

1434
01:52:03,920 --> 01:52:04,920
 tih korporacija.

1435
01:52:04,920 --> 01:52:05,880
 I tu on navodi,

1436
01:52:05,880 --> 01:52:06,640
 govori o tome.

1437
01:52:06,640 --> 01:52:09,100
 Covid-19, pa tu ne moram puno...

1438
01:52:09,100 --> 01:52:10,060
 To smo već sve...

1439
01:52:10,060 --> 01:52:11,480
 To svi znamo što je,

1440
01:52:11,480 --> 01:52:12,280
 kako je bilo

1441
01:52:12,280 --> 01:52:14,220
 i da je to naravno od ovih,

1442
01:52:14,220 --> 01:52:16,600
 danas čujemo od tih rukovodilaca,

1443
01:52:16,600 --> 01:52:19,160
 da je to bio njihov eksperiment

1444
01:52:19,160 --> 01:52:19,780
 najveći,

1445
01:52:19,780 --> 01:52:21,480
