1446
01:52:21,480 --> 01:52:22,520
 i tako dalje.

1447
01:52:22,520 --> 01:52:25,580
 Ali što se tu provijava

1448
01:52:25,580 --> 01:52:27,280
 u ovom kroz to što prolazi,

1449
01:52:27,280 --> 01:52:29,580
