01:52:32,180 --> 01:52:34,600
 metaverzum,

1452
01:52:34,600 --> 01:52:37,040
 drugo geek ekonomija,

1453
01:52:37,040 --> 01:52:40,640
 treće je transhumanizam,

1454
01:52:40,640 --> 01:52:41,500
 četvrto,

1455
01:52:41,500 --> 01:52:45,420
 što mi je četvrto tamo

1456
01:52:45,420 --> 01:52:50,360
 ulazi u ove digitalni formati,

1457
01:52:50,360 --> 01:52:53,480
 a to je znači digitalni tvrdi novčanik,

