01:52:59,360 --> 01:53:00,180
 Digitalni euro.

1461
01:53:00,180 --> 01:53:02,640
 Digitalna zdravstvena ova.

1462
01:53:02,640 --> 01:53:03,200
 Sve digi.

1463
01:53:03,200 --> 01:53:05,040
 A ne, digitalne novčaniki,

1464
01:53:05,040 --> 01:53:06,560
 ovaj digitalni novac

1465
01:53:06,560 --> 01:53:08,260
 i to je zajedno povezano,

1466
01:53:08,260 --> 01:53:09,040
 sve skupa, jel?

1467
01:53:09,440 --> 01:53:13,420
 I naravno još pet ili šesta stvar je

1468
01:53:13,420 --> 01:53:15,940
 da je Ursula von der Leyen

1469
01:53:15,940 --> 01:53:17,360
 potpisala,

1470
01:53:17,360 --> 01:53:18,040
 to je hrana,

1471
01:53:18,040 --> 01:53:19,780
 jer hrana uvijek važna svim ljudima,

1472
01:53:19,780 --> 01:53:21,060
 da te kukci,

1473
01:53:21,060 --> 01:53:22,060
 kukci,

1474
01:53:22,060 --> 01:53:24,580
 da brašno kukaca mogu se koristiti

1475
01:53:24,580 --> 01:53:25,220
 i tako dalje.

1476
01:53:25,220 --> 01:53:26,400
 E sad idemo,

1477
01:53:26,400 --> 01:53:28,020
