1481
01:53:34,460 --> 01:53:37,480
 o tome sve skupa

1482
01:53:37,480 --> 01:53:38,800
 i nude nam to,

1483
01:53:39,180 --> 01:53:39,680
 ali,

1484
01:53:39,680 --> 01:53:42,900
 ja sam se nasmijel,

1485
01:53:42,900 --> 01:53:44,320
 ali moram to reći,

1486
01:53:44,320 --> 01:53:45,480
 kaže ovako,

1487
01:53:45,480 --> 01:53:46,860
 znači da

1488
01:53:46,860 --> 01:53:51,220
 radnici moraju osloboditi kapital,

1489
01:53:51,220 --> 01:53:51,660
 pazite,

1490
01:53:51,660 --> 01:53:54,340
 radnici i narod moraju osloboditi kapital,

1491
01:53:54,340 --> 01:53:57,420
 kao da radnici i narod pritišću

1492
01:53:57,420 --> 01:54:00,080
