1551
01:56:15,800 --> 01:56:17,060
 Morao je, ti ću Mirovinu.

1552
01:56:17,060 --> 01:56:17,920
 Da, morao je, da.

1553
01:56:17,920 --> 01:56:19,040
 Vrijeme je, da.

1554
01:56:19,040 --> 01:56:23,040
 Međutim, ja sam gledao dnevni red Davosa,

1555
01:56:23,040 --> 01:56:24,300
