1580
01:57:43,340 --> 01:57:45,620
 Međutim, sada su se zaustavili.

1581
01:57:45,620 --> 01:57:48,380
 I sada je, osim Ursule Anders,

1582
01:57:48,880 --> 01:57:52,980
 von der Leyen, Ursule von der Leyen.

1583
01:57:52,980 --> 01:57:56,580
 Da, i Pfizer von der Leyen.

1584
01:57:56,580 --> 01:57:57,100
 Da, dobro.

