1598
01:58:35,760 --> 01:58:37,780
 kao što je Klaus Schwab radio,

1599
01:58:37,780 --> 01:58:39,240
 standardne, znači sve,

1600
01:58:39,240 --> 01:58:40,520
 novi svjetski poredak,

1601
01:58:40,520 --> 01:58:41,960
