1602
01:58:41,960 --> 01:58:43,360
 S druge strane,

1603
01:58:43,360 --> 01:58:45,820
 odbio je doći Guterres,

1604
01:58:45,820 --> 01:58:47,480
 generaciju uvijenih,

1605
01:58:47,480 --> 01:58:48,260
 to sam rekao,

1606
01:58:48,260 --> 01:58:49,020
 odbio je doći,

1607
01:58:49,020 --> 01:58:50,540
 kao bolestan, ne,

1608
01:58:50,540 --> 01:58:51,740
