1615
01:59:04,820 --> 01:59:06,600
 Zelenski se vratio u Davos

1616
01:59:06,600 --> 01:59:08,920
 i održao govor,

1617
01:59:08,920 --> 01:59:12,000
 međutim Zelenski je toliko

1618
01:59:12,000 --> 01:59:13,420
 bezobrazno govorio

1619
01:59:13,420 --> 01:59:16,080
