1624
01:59:21,380 --> 01:59:23,020
 da trebaju pomagati Ukrajina,

1625
01:59:23,020 --> 01:59:23,980
 trebamo još novo,

1626
01:59:23,980 --> 01:59:24,980
 treba ovo, ono,

1627
01:59:24,980 --> 01:59:27,020
 a da oni njemu ne pomagaju.

1628
01:59:27,020 --> 01:59:27,760
 A normalno,

1629
01:59:27,760 --> 01:59:30,340
 Trump je zaustavio financiranje,

1630
01:59:30,340 --> 01:59:33,040
 nakon toga je palo i financiranje

1631
