1635
01:59:44,080 --> 01:59:46,340
 I sada oni ne mogu postupiti.

1636
01:59:46,340 --> 01:59:48,540
 Oni su odobrili Ursula von der Leyen

1637
01:59:48,540 --> 01:59:50,340
 i dalje tjera staru politiku,

1638
01:59:50,340 --> 01:59:53,600
 jer ona sluša ovoga princa Charlesa,

1639
01:59:53,600 --> 01:59:54,740
 kralja Charlesa, pardon,

1640
01:59:54,740 --> 01:59:57,180
 i ona provodi tu politiku.

1641
01:59:57,180 --> 02:00:00,080
 i oni su odobrili 90 milijardi dolara

1642
02:00:00,080 --> 02:00:03,080
