1660
02:00:37,060 --> 02:00:39,720
 I tako slično radi sada i Trump,

1661
02:00:39,720 --> 02:00:40,960
 jel' po tome?

1662
02:00:40,960 --> 02:00:43,500
 Ali ovo je tih 800 milijarde,

1663
02:00:43,500 --> 02:00:45,880
