1680
02:01:20,860 --> 02:01:21,460
 Zašto?

1681
02:01:21,460 --> 02:01:22,180
 Pa rekao sam,

1682
02:01:22,180 --> 02:01:24,800
 90%, 95%

1683
02:01:24,800 --> 02:01:27,360
 NATO je u stvari američka vojska,

1684
02:01:27,360 --> 02:01:28,460
 američka oprava.

1685
02:01:28,460 --> 02:01:29,580
 Druga stvar,

1686
02:01:29,580 --> 02:01:31,080
 bio je ovoj Vitkov

1687
02:01:31,080 --> 02:01:32,740
 i kak se zove ovoj...

1688
02:01:32,740 --> 02:01:33,060
 Kusner.

1689
02:01:33,060 --> 02:01:34,780
 Kusner.

1690
02:01:34,780 --> 02:01:37,960
 Kusner, tako je, to je ovaj zet od ovoga Trumpa,

1691
02:01:37,960 --> 02:01:40,500
 koji još jedan su, još jednog su savjetnika.

1692
02:01:40,500 --> 02:01:41,440
 Bili su u Moskvi.

1693
02:01:41,440 --> 02:01:43,720
 Bili su u Moskvi, pa su bili sad ovaj,

1694
02:01:43,720 --> 02:01:45,960
